    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think 100 and 50% make sense as defaults. A lot of people are coming from OE, so keeping the same ones will result in similar behaviour which is nice. These estimates are not as reliable as 3rd party estimates, so their use is somewhat limited anyways. \r\n\r\nAgreed that empty blocks should be part of the calculation and if the last 100 blocks are empty, then reverting to the minimum makes sense. ",
